text: Freddy Jensen (28 January 1926 - 9 April 1996) was a Danish gymnast. He competed at the 1948 Summer Olympics and the 1952 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1926 births Category:1996 deaths Category:Danish male artistic gymnasts Category:Olympic gymnasts of Denmark Category:Gymnasts at the 1948 Summer Olympics Category:Gymnasts at the 1952 Summer Olympics Category:People from Nuuk
